moji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb2101dac0e6b5d6f8e12c272346177320a92f1","tid":230841,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:39:10.000Z","msg":"book完先知係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有巴打話間屋擺埋leaflet，叫你唔好同鄰居眼神交流，又要等冇人先搭lift上樓<br />\n我6月頭去東京，book咗間涉谷附近嘅airbnb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n420蚊晚，間屋都夠大，揀咗superhost，host係日本人<br />\n唔驚得咁多，同價錢嘅酒店單人房細到勉強開到喼"},{"pid":"30ff957a127621cc46f76602495aff45b42175e3","tid":230841,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"唔會理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8310ba86e6815e5e166b21c24c593fe5b8f98e","tid":230841,"uid":46584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T08:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>book完先知係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有巴打話間屋擺埋leaflet，叫你唔好同鄰居眼神交流，又要等冇人先搭lift上樓<br />\n我6月頭去東京，book咗間涉谷附近嘅airbnb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n420蚊晚，間屋都夠大，揀咗superhost，host係日本人<br />\n唔驚得咁多，同價錢嘅酒店單人房細到勉強開到喼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係book左airbnb，依家好驚出發前佢同我取消左，到時book酒店就貴到仆街，洗靚個菊花都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}